README.md
     1‚Üí# xxhash
     6‚Üíxxhash is a Go implementation of the 64-bit [xxHash] algorithm, XXH64. This is a
     7‚Üíhigh-quality hashing algorithm that is much faster than anything in the Go
     8‚Üístandard library.
     9‚Üí
    10‚ÜíThis package provides a straightforward API:
    11‚Üí
    12‚Üí```
    13‚Üífunc Sum64(b []byte) uint64
    14‚Üífunc Sum64String(s string) uint64
    15‚Üítype Digest struct{ ... }
    16‚Üí    func New() *Digest
    17‚Üí```
    18‚Üí
    19‚ÜíThe `Digest` type implements hash.Hash64. Its key methods are:
    20‚Üí
    21‚Üí```
    22‚Üífunc (*Digest) Write([]byte) (int, error)
    23‚Üífunc (*Digest) WriteString(string) (int, error)
    24‚Üífunc (*Digest) Sum64() uint64
    25‚Üí```
    26‚Üí
