    33‚Üí## Compatibility
    35‚ÜíThis package is in a module and the latest code is in version 2 of the module.
    36‚ÜíYou need a version of Go with at least "minimal module compatibility" to use
    37‚Üígithub.com/cespare/xxhash/v2:
    38‚Üí
